ZH: 怎么样？今天心情怎么样？
EN: How are you? How is your mood today?

ZH: 怎么去那家餐厅？
EN: How do I get to that restaurant?

ZH: 你觉得怎么样？
EN: What do you think?

ZH: 怎么帮助你？
EN: How can I help you?

ZH: 我怎么能忘记那个美丽的风景呢？
EN: How could I forget that beautiful scenery?

ZH: 你怎么能这么健康？
EN: How can you be so healthy?

ZH: 他怎么知道我们的计划？
EN: How did he know about our plan?

ZH: 这样做怎么会有好结果呢？
EN: How can this lead to a good outcome?

ZH: 你觉得这种颜色怎么样？
EN: What do you think of this color?

ZH: 怎么才能到达最终目的地？
EN: How can we reach the final destination?

ZH: 怎么解释这个现象呢？
EN: How do you explain this phenomenon?

ZH: 他们怎么能这么快完成工作？
EN: How can they finish the work so quickly?

ZH: 这个数学题怎么做？
EN: How do you solve this math problem?

ZH: 这部电影怎么样？值得一看吗？
EN: How is this movie? Is it worth watching?

ZH: 怎么保持身体健康？
EN: How to maintain a healthy body?

ZH: 你们怎么准备这个会议的？
EN: How are you preparing for this meeting?

ZH: 怎么才能让孩子更专注？
EN: How can we make the children more focused?

ZH: 他怎么会这么失望呢？
EN: How could he be so disappointed?

ZH: 怎么才能提高生产效率？
EN: How can we improve production efficiency?

ZH: 这件事情怎么会发生？
EN: How could this happen?
